data.description: Move-in ready ranch in Bellefontaine!  Home features a living room with wood floors, large eat-in kitchen, 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths all on the main level plus a finished partial basement with a rec/family room, fireplace, laundry area and a full bathroom.  There is a covered patio and small fenced backyard plus an upper tier section of additional yard with mature trees (lot size: 80x140'). The property is nicely landscaped and has a manicured lawn.  Home is located in Glenwood Allotment #5 in the Whispering Pines area of Bellefontaine.  Call today for your appointment!
